## Third-Party Data

### Quranic Text — Tanzil.net

**Source:** [Tanzil.net](https://tanzil.net)

**Source files (from Tanzil.net):**
- `public/data/quran-simple.txt` — Arabic text (quran-simple edition)
- `public/data/en.sahih.txt` — Sahih International English translation
- `public/data/en.transliteration.txt` — English transliteration

**Derived files (project structure, Tanzil.net data):**
- `public/data/quran.json` — Consolidated Quran data built from source files above

The `quran.json` file is generated by project scripts (CC BY-NC 4.0), but the Quranic text and translations within it originate from Tanzil.net and remain subject to their terms.

**Terms:** Permission is granted by Tanzil.net to copy and distribute verbatim copies of the Quran text. The text in this repository is distributed unmodified from the original source.

**Attribution:** The Quranic text and translations in this project are provided by the [Tanzil Project](https://tanzil.net). Users of this data must:
1. Clearly indicate Tanzil.net as the source
2. Provide a link to https://tanzil.net

For the most up-to-date text and any corrections, please refer to the original source at tanzil.net.

